   NATIONAL
</P>
<P>
   BUSH-FLA _ George W. Bush campaigns at Florida International
University in Miami on a second day of a trip to the Sunshine
State. (Crowley, Palm Beach Post).
</P>
<P>
   JONBENET _ ATLANTA _The giant spotlight that follows the
JonBenet Ramsey case will shift to Atlanta Monday, as the slain
girl's parents speak once again with investigators who've probed
the case for over three years. The prospect of Ramseys walking out
of the interviews in handcuffs, or of the police clearing the
couple of suspicion , remain doubtful, according to both sides. But
Boulder, Colo., Police Chief Mark Beckner insists that new
questions - not new evidence - have arisen. (Schneider, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
