<TEXT>
<P>
   SCHOOL-NETSUBSIDY _ A federal program that allows private
schools to get millions of dollars in Internet subsidies has the
backing of Al Gore but is being opposed by George W. Bush -- a
reversal of the two parties' stands on providing public funding for
school choice programs. About 1,500
</P>
</TEXT>
