   FBC-GATECH _ ATLANTA _ Advancing Sunday night's Ga. Tech-Va.
Tech game. Is this the Renaissance of Georgia Tech football. It
just might be. Under the direction of head coach George O'Leary,
Tech has jumped into national prominence. It has defeated Georgia
in back to back seasons. It has recruited several good classes,
including last year's that was ranked in the top 10. It is adding
seats to its stadium. O'Leary discusses how he feels about the
program ... where Tech has improved, where it needs to go. (Arey,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution) 25.
