Rees-Mogg, co-managers of the $322 million Eaton Vance Information
Age Fund. Investing in the technology, media and telecommunications
sector, or TMT as it is known, ``does not have to be an extreme
sport,'' insisted Richardson. By Joanne Legomsky.
