<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-25 20:57 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2482 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i BC-ISRAEL-ASSESS-2TAKES(     08-25 0826
