PETS: As if the experience of flying wasn't bad enough for
two-legged travelers, now their four-legged friends are feeling the
pinch as well. Amid continuing labor problems, United Airlines has
announced that a summertime embargo on checking in pets as baggage
will be extended indefinitely. BY DAVID LAZARUS (running in main
news). &QL; 
 &QL; 
